body: forward_numpyop forward_numpyop(ops:List[op.numpyop.numpyop.NumpyOp], data:MutableMapping[str, Any], mode:str) -> None Call the forward function for list of NumpyOps, and modify the data dictionary in place. Args: ops : A list of NumpyOps to execute. data : The data dictionary. mode : The current execution mode ("train", "eval", "test", or "infer").
